# Concision &mdash; Primes in Java

```java
public final class Primes {
  public static boolean isPrime(int n) {
    var isPrime = true;
    var max = (int) Math.ceil(Math.sqrt(n));
    for (int i = 2; i <= max; ++i) {
      if (n % i == 0) {
        isPrime = false;
        break;
      }
    }
    return isPrime;
  }
}
```
